OL,3,CWater quality of two bathing spots
OL,4,Cmarked as 'too poor' for swimming
OL,6,FSixteen water spots have been tested
OL,7,Fin Cumbria, both Derwentwater at Crow
OL,8,FPark and the Boating Centre at
OL,9,FConiston Water were both deemed
OL,10,Funsuitable for bathing.
OL,12,FThe tests monitor for sources of
OL,13,Fpollution known to be a risk to the
OL,14,Fhealth of swimmers, specifically E.
OL,15,Fcoli and intestinal enterococci, which
OL,16,Fare two types of bacteria found in
OL,17,Fhuman and animal excrement.
