OL,3,CWater quality of two bathing spots
OL,4,Cmarked as 'too poor' for swimming
OL,6,FTwenty-seven new bathing water sites
OL,7,Fwere tested this year, 18 of which
OL,8,Fwere marked as 'poor', meaning they do
OL,9,Fnot meet the minimum standard of water
OL,10,Fquality.
OL,12,FThe Environment Agency say this is a
OL,13,Fcommon issue with new tests due to the
OL,14,Fareas being monitored for the first
OL,15,Ftime, stating it takes time to
OL,16,Funderstand the sources of pollution
OL,17,Faffecting them.
