OL,6,FShe said: "That's why we are placing
OL,7,Fwater companies under special measures
OL,8,Fthrough the Water Bill, which will
OL,9,Fstrengthen regulation including new
OL,10,Fpowers to ban the payment of bonuses
OL,11,Ffor polluting water bosses and bring
OL,12,Fcriminal charges against persistent
OL,13,Flaw breakers.
OL,15,F"This is just the start ` we've
OL,16,Flaunched the largest review of the
OL,17,Fwater sector since privatisation to
OL,18,Fattract the investment we need and
OL,19,Freform the water system to help clean
OL,20,Fup our rivers, lakes and seas for
OL,21,Fgood."
