OL,6,FSixty-three prosecutions have been
OL,7,Fbrought upon water and sewerage
OL,8,Fcompanies, securing fines of more than
OL,9,F#151m since 2015.
OL,11,F16 areas across Cumbria were assessed
OL,12,Fin this year's English coastal and
OL,13,Finland bathing waters review:
OL,15,FThe Environment Agency takes up to 20
OL,16,Fwater samples at each designed
OL,17,Fswimming spot site during the review.
